      ]]></graph-entry-excerpt>
      <dependency-contract-summaries>
        <dependency-1 module="M-AUDIT-LOG">Structured audit logger with required redaction-safe fields and stable markers.</dependency-1>
      </dependency-contract-summaries>
      <verification-excerpt><![CDATA[
